      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Key Features That Make Dify Stand Out",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "There are other LLM platforms out there. LangChain, Flowise, Langflow — I've tried them all. Here's where Dify pulls ahead:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Visual Workflow Builder That Actually Works",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Some platforms give you a canvas that's more confusing than writing code. Dify's workflow editor is clean, responsive, and intuitive. You drag nodes, connect them with edges, and configure each one in a side panel. It handles branching, loops, parallel execution, and error handling gracefully.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I built a customer support agent that checks a knowledge base, escalates to a human if confidence is low, and logs every interaction — all in under an hour.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Multi-Model Support Without Vendor Lock-In",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Switch from GPT-4 to Claude to Llama 3 with a dropdown. Seriously. Each node in a workflow can use a different model. This is huge for cost optimization — use a cheap model for simple tasks and a powerful one for complex reasoning.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Built-In RAG Pipeline",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The retrieval system is production-grade. It supports multiple chunking strategies, embedding models, and retrieval methods (hybrid search, reranking). You upload your docs, tweak a few settings, and you have a working knowledge base in minutes.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One-Click API Deployment",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every app you build in Dify becomes an API endpoint automatically. Embed it in your website, connect it to Slack, integrate it with Zapier — whatever you need. There's also a ready-made chatbot widget you can drop into any page.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Collaboration Features",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Teams can work together on the same projects. There's role-based access control, version history, and environment separation (dev/staging/prod). This matters when you're building AI apps for a business, not just experimenting.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
