            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — Dify now supports true agentic behavior where nodes can dynamically decide what to do next based on LLM reasoning. This goes beyond static flowcharts. Your agents can loop, branch, and adapt in real time.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Plugin Ecosystem",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " — The marketplace is growing with community-built plugins. Google Search, Stable Diffusion, Wolfram Alpha, and custom tools are all available as drag-and-drop components.",
