        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Your company wants to add AI features to existing products. Dify gives your team a shared platform to experiment, build, and deploy without every project requiring a dedicated ML engineer.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Developers Who Want Speed",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "You know how to code. You could build this from scratch. But why spend three weeks on infrastructure when Dify handles the plumbing and you focus on the logic?",
